Airline Booking Market Demand Dashboard
This is a simple Python web app built with Streamlit to visualize airline booking trends using mock data.

#### Features
- Filter by destination
- View demand trends using line charts
- See top routes and peak demand dates

#### Tech Stack
- Python
- Streamlit
- Pandas
- Plotly

#### Folder Structure
airline-demand-dashboard
├── app.py
├── requirements.txt
├── data
│ └── sample_data.csv
└── utils
└── data_processing.py
#### How to Run
Open the terminal and run this commands
Step 1. Install required libraries
Step 2. pip install -r requirements.txt
Step 3. streamlit run app.py

